        513.09,
        358.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p142_s0012",
      "text": "4.2.49",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        454.96,
        123.76,
        466.08
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p142_s0013",
      "text": "FFI Registered Map Update Notification (FFI_RMUN)",
      "bbox": [
        133.83,
        454.96,
        380.34,
        466.08
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p142_s0014",
      "text": "4.2.49.1  Description",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        478.96,
        192.69,
        490.08
      ],
      "block_index": 8,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p142_s0015",
      "text": "A unidirectional FFI_RMUN Request shall be sent to registered Nx_Ports (see 4.2.48) when the AE",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        502.96,
        539.88,
        514.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p142_s0016",
      "text": "Principal Switch sends an Fast Fabric Initialization (FFI) Request Sequence initiated by the AE Prin-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        514.96,
        540.09,
        526.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p142_s0017",
      "text": "cipal Switch. ",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        526.96,
        154.35,
        538.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p142_s0018",
      "text": "Support for this ELS is mandatory for a Domain Controller in an AE Principal Switch or an AE Switch",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        550.96,
        540.08,
        562.08
      ],
      "block_index": 10,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p142_s0019",
      "text": "that is capable of becoming an AE Principal Switch. Support for this ELS is optional for Nx_Ports.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        562.96,
        539.9,
        574.08
      ],
      "block_index": 10,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p142_s0020",
      "text": "However, if the Nx_Port invokes the FFI_MUR ELS, it shall support receipt of the FFI_RMUN Re-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        574.96,
        540.17,
        586.08
      ],
      "block_index": 10,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p142_s0021",
      "text": "quest.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        586.96,
        123.17,
        598.08
      ],
      "block_index": 10,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p142_s0022",
      "text": "FFI_RMUN Request is intended to provide a timely indication of Map Updates to avoid the consider-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        610.96,
        540.06,
        622.08
      ],
      "block_index": 11,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p142_s0023",
      "text": "able time to discover any such failure. ",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        622.96,
        265.96,
        634.08
      ],
      "block_index": 11,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p142_s0024",
      "text": "Sending FFI_RMUN Requests between Nx_Ports is prohibited. Sending FFI_RMUN Requests by a",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        647.02,
        539.94,
        658.14
      ],
      "block_index": 12,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p142_s0025",
      "text": "Domain Controller that is not an AE Principal Switch is prohibited.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        659.02,
        385.36,
        670.14
      ],
      "block_index": 12,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
